"FlappyBird.instructions" = "# Flappy Bird\n\nKeep the bird flying through gaps in oncoming pipes.\n\n## How to play\n\n- **Tap anywhere** to flap. Each tap gives the bird a small upward boost.\n- Without taps, gravity pulls the bird down.\n- Fly through the gap between each pair of pipes to score a point.\n\n## Game over\n\nThe game ends if the bird hits a pipe, the ground, or the top of the screen.\n\n## Tips\n\n- Tap rhythmically — short, even taps are easier to control than panicked spamming.\n- Aim for the middle of each gap so you have room to react to the next one.";
